data.title: Taoyuan()
data.text:
The Taoyuan Branch located at Taiwan Taoyuan International Airport, with four inspection stations in Taoyuan and Hsinchu. The Branch is responsible for quarantine inspection of animals, plants and their products carried by freight and passengers, as well as supervising of sanitation at slaughterhouses of domestic and poultry in Taoyuan City , Hsinchu City and County, and Miao-li County .
